HEADWORD: blackberry-lily
<hw>blackberry-lily</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>garden plant whose capsule
discloses when ripe a mass of seeds resembling a blackberry.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> leopard lily, Belamcanda chinensis.</syn>⟦br⟧
